snippet.title: Vivid Surf | Slippery Slopes
snippet.description:
One of the trickier parts of the first 'Ascension' map
(Hopefully, you don't end up falling here)

Vivid surf is a singleplayer focused game exploring new areas of surf style movement, using unreal engine 5

Wishlist on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1288580/Vivid_Surf/
